export const questionObj = {"Qtext": "
 
Find the mean proportion of 2.8 and 0.7 
\newline

", "Steps": [{"id": "s1", "n_params": 0, "step_txt": "$$\text{
 
The mean proportion of 2.8 and 0.7 is $\sqrt{2.8 \times 0.7 }$.
\[
	= \sqrt{\frac{28.0 \times 7.0 }{100}} = \frac{14 }{10} = 1.4 
\]
Since, 
\[
	28.0 \times 7.0 = 196 = 14 ^2
\]
\newline
}$$
"}]} 

 export const resp = [{"data": [], "text": ""}]
